The paper proposes a multimodal variational autoencoder for weakly supervised learning, which involves learning joint representations of multiple modalities. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and multimedia (cs.MM). However, given that the paper focuses on generative models and deep learning, as well as its emphasis on image transformations, we believe that cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories. The other sub-categories are also possible, but may be less likely given the specific focus of the paper.
